IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: PROVIDING AFFORDABLE PRIMARY CARE TO THOSE WHO NEED IT MOST IN THE GREATER PHOENIX AREA.
IRS990.MissionDesc: MOUNTAIN PARK HEALTH CENTER WORKS WITH THE COMMUNITIES IT SERVES TO SUSTAIN AND IMPROVE HEALTH BY PROVIDING AFFORDABLE PRIMARY CARE TO THOSE WHO NEED IT MOST. OUR COMMITMENT TO THE COMMUNITY IS TO KEEP HEALTHCARE AFFORDABLE AND ACCESSIBLE.
IRS990.Desc: MOUNTAIN PARK HEALTH CENTER PROVIDES HEALTH RELATED SERVICES TO UNINSURED PATIENTS IN CARRYING OUT ITS TAX-EXEMPT PURPOSE AS A PRIMARY CARE FACILITY. IN 1984, MOUNTAIN PARK HEALTH CENTER BEGAN SERVING THE COMMUNITY WITH ONE DOCTOR AND ONE CLINIC LOCATION. TODAY, OUR COMMUNITY HEALTH CENTER HAS MULTIPLE CLINICS IN DIVERSE NEIGHBORHOODS ACROSS THE VALLEY, INCLUDING PRIMARY MEDICAL, DENTAL, PHARMACEUTICAL, AND INTEGRATED HEALTH CARE.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: CUSTODIAL ARRANGEMENTS: THE ORGANIZATION HOLDS SECURITY DEPOSITS FOR TENANTS WHO LEASE SPACE IN A BUILDING. THE FUNDS ARE HELD IN A BANK ACCOUNT UNTIL RETURNED TO THE TENANT. FUNDS ARE REFUNDED TO TENANTS UPON TERMINATION OF THE LEASE.

UNCERTAIN TAX POSITIONS: MANAGEMENT HAS EVALUATED THEIR INCOME TAX POSITIONS UNDER GUIDANCE INCLUDED IN ASC 740. BASED ON THEIR REVIEW, MANAGEMENT HAS NOT IDENTIFIED ANY MATERIAL UNCERTAIN TAX POSITIONS TO BE RECORDED OR DISCLOSED IN THE FINANCIAL STATEMENTS.
NONQUALIFIED RETIREMENT PLAN: A 457(F) PLAN WAS ESTABLISHED BEGINNING JANUARY 1, 2017, FOR JOHN SWAGERT, MD. VESTED DATE WITH SINGLE LUMP-SUM CASH PAYMENT OF $281,822 ON 12/31/21.

PURPOSE OF BOND: TO FINANCE THE CONSTRUCTION, IMPROVEMENT, AND EQUIPPING OF HEALTH CARE FACILITIES FOR USE BY THE BORROWER; TO REFINANCE CERTAIN OF THE BORROWER'S OUTSTANDING OBLIGATIONS FOR THE ACQUISITION AND CONSTRUCTION OF PRIOR HEALTH CARE FACILITIES AND OPERATING EXPENSES; AND TO PAY THE COSTS OF ISSUANCES OF THE SERIES 2014 BONDS.
THE REBATE COMPUTATION WAS PERFORMED ON 02/27/2019.
NUMBER OF CONTRIBUTIONS: THE NUMBER ENTERED IN COLUMN B REPRESENTS THE COUNT OF SEPARATE DONATIONS FROM ONE DONOR DURING THE YEAR.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 11B
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: 990 REVIEW POLICY: THE FORM 990 IS PREPARED BY AN INDEPENDENT ACCOUNTING FIRM BASED ON THE AUDITED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE ACCOUNTING DEPARTMENT OF THE ORGANIZATION. PRIOR TO FILING, THE FORM 990 IS REVIEWED BY THE FINANCE AND AUDIT COMMITTEES. ONCE THEY HAVE APPROVED THE DRAFT, A FINAL DRAFT IS PRESENTED AND APPROVED BY THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS PRIOR TO FILING.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 12C
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: MONITORING COMPLIANCE WITH CONFLICT OF INTEREST POLICY: BOARD MEMBERS ANNUALLY REVIEW AND SIGN A CONFLICT OF INTEREST STATEMENT. POTENTIAL CONFLICTS ARE BROUGHT TO THE FULL BOARD FOR A DETERMINATION OF WHETHER A CONFLICT EXISTS. EMPLOYEES ARE REQUIRED TO ANNUALLY SIGN A CONFLICT OF INTEREST STATEMENT TO DISCLOSE POTENTIAL CONFLICTS. IF THE SITUATION IS UNCLEAR, THE CEO DETERMINES WHETHER A CONFLICT EXISTS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 15A & 15B
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: COMPENSATION REVIEW POLICY: SALARIES ARE DETERMINED BY A COMBINATION OF PERFORMANCE EFFECTIVENESS REVIEWS AND SALARY SURVEY DATA FOR COMPARABLE JOBS COMPILED BY AN INDEPENDENT FIRM. THE SALARIES OF THE CEO ARE SET UP AND REVIEWED ANNUALLY BY THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS AND COMPARED TO SURVEY DATA FOR COMPARABLE JOBS. THE LAST COMPENSATION REVIEW OCCURRED IN JUNE OF 2022. FOR ANYONE OTHER THAN THE CEO, THE PROCESS IS OVERSEEN BY THE COO AND HR DIRECTOR. INDEPENDENT INFORMATION, COMPARABILITY, DATA, ETC. IS OBTAINED FOR ALL STAFF, INCLUDING KEY OFFICERS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION C, LINE 19
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: DOCUMENT DISCLOSURE: THE ORGANIZATION'S GOVERNING DOCUMENTS, CONFLICT OF INTEREST POLICY, AND FINANCIAL STATEMENTS ARE MADE AVAILABLE UPON REQUEST.
